description:
Since attacks began in Ukraine on the morning of February 24, 2022, thousands of Ukrainian refugees fled the country, looking for refuge in neighbouring regions.

In the midst of the crisis, the Adventist church in Romania has been beacon of light by providing assistance to incoming refugees. As a result of the love and support they have received, many refugees have accepted Jesus as Lord of their lives.

Find this story and others on our Youtube channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/AdventistOrgChurch
